{"tid":1293577,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】便衣警戴頭盔、持圓盾清場　稱執行職務毋須展示委任證","createTime":"2019-07-07T16:20:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T17:57:43.000Z","uid":66271,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"49083e0409a6875290fca32d0fba703b18e82b3a","tid":1293577,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:20:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/2101759856619065/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fvideos%2F2101759856619065%2F&d=P0gT%2F24t7mhr82HgIt0JlRX1SmvCJyfLMOcbfj5ioUM%3D&h=395b3360\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/2101759856619065/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/waiwai-11_8mmDT_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fwaiwai-11_8mmDT_1200x0.png&h=e65c484c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n晚上近11時警方清場，在旺角彌敦道以「包抄」方式前後包圍示威者，現場多次爆發衝突。《立場新聞》拍攝到，有身穿便衣的警員，戴頭盔、持圓盾參與清場行動，並沒展示警員編號或委任證。有市民質疑他的身份時，該警員高呼：「警察執行職務時，係唔需要展示委任證！」<br />\n<br />\n晚上近11時，該名警員身處彌敦道，他身穿便服，卻穿戴寫有「Police」字眼的頭盔及圓盾，身上並沒有警員編號或委任證。他聯同多名軍裝警參與清場行動，與示威者對峙。<br />\n<br />\n示威者多次質疑他的身份，並要求他出示委任證，「都唔知你係唔係差佬」。該便衣警員激動地高呼：「警察執行職務時，係唔需要展示委任證！」示威者隨即向他喝倒采。<br />\n<br />\n根據警方網站資料顯示，便衣人員與巿民接觸時，不論是否當值，在行使警察權力時，必須表明身分及出示委任證。如市民提出要求，軍裝警務人員須出示委任證，除了三種情況。第一是「情況不容許」出示；或第二是「出示委任證會影響警隊行動及/或危及有關人員的安全」；或第三是「要求不合理」。<br />\n<br />\n《立場新聞》正就事件向警方查詢，尚待回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一哥可唔可以解釋下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d74c4cc8a3947281033de5dab7ef316edd85519f","tid":1293577,"uid":197163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:30:57.000Z","msg":"搞大佢"},{"pid":"385b0151bc1ed367fcb6fd7de6e1cce4345d3cee","tid":1293577,"uid":66271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d74c4cc8a3947281033de5dab7ef316edd85519f","tid":1293577,"uid":197163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:30:57.000Z","msg":"搞大佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T17:09:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/66140332_1427813677357648_776340017634082816_n.jpg?_nc_cat=107&amp;_nc_oc=AQlCLvVJrTb-1EhEWgfl0MLfxsRlgyhsVQjp6KSMCNCOUvqNjqKzuWEqCuW5lZgpY9RV0lEDBhNsf6IwLtEazyv5&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-1.xx&amp;oh=3949b185ef0e0d72d1beb7aebf51a61c&amp;oe=5DB92C0C\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F66140332_1427813677357648_776340017634082816_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D107%26_nc_oc%3DAQlCLvVJrTb-1EhEWgfl0MLfxsRlgyhsVQjp6KSMCNCOUvqNjqKzuWEqCuW5lZgpY9RV0lEDBhNsf6IwLtEazyv5%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-1.xx%26oh%3D3949b185ef0e0d72d1beb7aebf51a61c%26oe%3D5DB92C0C&h=d8a15b29&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5af03f901429287f3bc9fa537398822e662fdd73","tid":1293577,"uid":150753,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T17:55:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9c841722cd4aecfe3343afc0eca11b6e31809745","tid":1293577,"uid":264245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T17:57:43.000Z","msg":"不久既將會有好多有心既警察遊行"}]}